#X text 837 115 RECORDING: \; - WHEN LAUNCHED \, IF RECORD-Q IS ON \, SEQUENCER WILL START "LISTENING" TO THE INCOMING TRIGGERS \; - BAR-TIME SUBPATCH IS CONTINUOUSLY OUTPUTTING BAR-TIME FROM 0[ms] AT LAUNCH UNTIL BAR-DURATION REACHED \; - THE BAR-TIME IS DIVIDED BY BAR-DURATION TO BASICALLY SAVE PLAYBACK POSITION IN THE BAR AS A RATIO (BAR-DURATION-IRRELEVANT) \; - THE RATIO IS CONTINUOUSLY WRITTEN IN FLOAT OBJECT AND WHEN "LISTENING" IF TRIGGER ARRIVES THE TIME OF THE BANG WILL BE INSERTED TO THE END OF \$0-sequence \;, f 70;
#X text 838 279 PLAYBACK: \; - WHEN LAUNCHED \, FIRST THING THE \$0-SEQUENCE WILL BE SORTED AND THEN FIRST ELEMENT IN THE \$0-SEQUENCE WILL BE "GET" AND WRITTEN INTO EXPRESSION. ALSO TOGGLE OF SPIGOT WILL BE TURNED ON (WAITING FOR BAR-TIME REACHING THE GET VALUE) \; - WITH BAR-TIME RUNNING AS SOON AS IT REACHES THE GET VALUE \, 1) IT WILL OUTPUT A BANG \, 2) TURN OFF THE TOGGLE (OTHERWISE BANGS WILL CONTINUE) \, 3)OUTPUTS NEXT ELEMENT IN \$0-SEQUENCE AND 4)TURNS ON THE TOGGLE \; ** NOTE-1: IF NO ELEMENT EXIST FOR THE INPUT (EX: ONLY 2 ELEMENT EXIST AND REQUESTING 3RD) TEXT GET OBJECT WILL OUTPUT NOTHING AND SO TOGGLE STAYS OFF! \; ** NOTE-2: THE REASON THAT WE DO NOT HAVE A SIMPLE "EQUAL EXPRESSION" INSTEAD OF ALL THE LOWER PART OF PLAYBACK IS THAT PRECISION IS NOT TRUSTABLE AND IT IS NOT SURE THAT WE HIT EXACTLY THE VALUE TO OUTPUT A BANG... \;;
